snippet.textDisplay:
Look I hate being the negative guy, and I am sure Dennis is a great employee, but he is a terrible host.  He is better than the last time he hosted, but it really dosnt matter how comfortable he gets on camera, it is his accent.  He is hard to understand.  I know that is not his fault, like I said I am sure he is a great employee, and from everything I have seen a good person, all that said it still dosnt mean I have to enjoy his videos. 

Everyone at LMG from what I have seen has a good personality, and I would be more than happy to watch Dennis if he was easier to understand.  Get him a language coach or keep him off camera.
